Key Concepts Summary
Concept	Purpose
Resource Requests	Minimum resources needed
Resource Limits	Maximum resources allowed
ResourceQuota	Limit resources in one namespace
Object Quota	Limit number of objects
ClusterResourceQuota	Limit resources across namespaces
